cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper deals with medical image segmentation using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of heteroscedastic networks, which are a type of neural network architecture used in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves the use of data augmentation and the examination of loss functions, which are common topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper deals with medical imaging, which is a sub-topic of multimedia (cs.MM).
